        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>A new extended life fan belt design for Caterpillar C-15 engines used in International&#174; 9200i
                    and 9400i Models built after October, 2002 has been released for production and service. The new
                    design fan belt, Part Number 3565413
                    <emph type="bold">C3</emph>
                    replaces the current belt, Part number 3565413
                    <emph type="bold">C2</emph>.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
        <partsinfo>
            <table id="t0612091">
