                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>3565413C3</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
        </partsinfo>
        <svcproc svcproctype="repair" graphiccount="0">
            <title>Service procedure</title>
            <specpara>
                <warning>
                    <para>To avoid property damage, personal injury, or death, park the vehicle on a flat level surface,
                        set the parking brake, turn the engine off, and chock the wheels.
                    </para>
                </warning>
            </specpara>
            <specpara>
                <warning>
                    <para>To avoid personal injury or death, allow the engine to cool sufficiently before performing
                        service.
                    </para>
                </warning>
            </specpara>
            <para>Replace the fan belt following standard belt replacement procedures.</para>
        </svcproc>
